summary: This document appears to be a confidential communication from AT&T regarding the inability to obtain location information for a specific mobile number. It discusses potential reasons for the lack of data and provides guidance on interpreting the results. The document emphasizes caution in using the location data for investigative purposes.
keyFacts: The document is a confidential communication from AT&T.
It discusses the inability to obtain position information for a mobile number.
Reasons for lack of data include the mobile being powered off or out of service area.
The document advises caution in using location data for investigative purposes.
No specific individuals are mentioned in the document.
